name: Fish or Famine
description:
NOTICE

The high-score mechanic has been mad in a browser, so if you reset it, the high-score will be gone.

Rules

You have a fishing rod, your goal is to catch the fish, but your fishing string can be bitten off by fishes, so don't go too low because a lot of fishes can bite it off. But you might want to go down, because there is a shield, that protects your fishing rod from being bitten off for 5 seconds. And also, you can't just stay at the top, there is a 1 minute timer so don't waste time!
